## Common Patterns
- Entry points always export `{ mount, unmount }` using `createMountPair`
- Vite configs use extension name in base path and output directory
- CSS files go in `src/assets/main.css` and `src/assets/base.css`
- All extensions use Vue 3 + Vite + TypeScript
